						<a class="reply" href="http://forums.bit-tech.net/newreply.php?do=newreply&amp;p=2277644"  target="_blank" title="Quote"><img src="http://images.bit-tech.net/images/reply.gif" alt="Quote" /></a>
					</div>

					<div class="commentCopy">Normally having to check off for an additional clause should sound some alarms. It may be hard to read Legalese but at least a slight brush over should alert you when words like "immortal" and "soul" come up. It's a good lesson to teach people, don't just take things for granted. Very well done by GameStation!</div>
				</div>
